..TEXT:
It is the spirit of Guido da Montefeltro that
speaks.  The city of Montefeltro lies between Urbino and that
part of the Apennines in which the Tiber rises.  Count Guido was
a famous warrior, and one of the great Ghibelline leaders.  He
tells his own story sufficiently in detail in what follows.
