..TEXT:
The arms of Guido da Polenta, Lord of Ravenna,
Dante's friend, and father (or nephew) of Francesca da Rimini,
were an eagle half white in a field of azure, and half red in a
field of gold.  Cervia is a small town some twelve miles from
Ravenna.
